microprocessor_definition.description: Controller for door with lock and 90deg open

object.script:
function onTick() doorAngleIn = input.getNumber(1) doorLockIn = input.getBool(2) doorControl = input.getBool(3)
if doorControl then --Switch on openDoor() else closeDoor() end end
function openDoor() output.setBool(8, false) --Open lock output.setNumber(7, 1) --Open door full end
function closeDoor() output.setNumber(7, 0) --Close Door -- while doorAngleIn > 0 do --Wait for door close
-- end output.setBool(8, true) --Lock door end

end
